sequenceDiagram
    participant Browser
    participant Gateway
    participant Auth
    participant API
    participant Mongo
    participant Kafka
    participant Pinot

    Browser->>Gateway: GraphQL Query
    Gateway->>Auth: Validate JWT
    Gateway->>API: Forward request
    API->>Mongo: Fetch domain data
    API-->>Browser: Response

    API->>Kafka: Publish event
    Kafka->>Pinot: Analytics ingestion
